oYyehu?filename=bjj3Xo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbjj3Xo8.png&h=7de0224f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcerAgrBzRAHCUTxWQNV9KjU7uCD4M5eDkJYr2fGthnpP?filename=MKckZDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKckZDL.png&h=fb6729c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTamFJ91LHB2ztq1cVwUnoNpC8zEymFryPTJaCPpsoAav?filename=4cqR6hu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cqR6hu.png&h=d0bb26b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主條死賤種亂咁屈人五毛 分化手足<br />\n屈完又唔肯同每個受害者道歉<br />\n仲要搵藉口話自己覆錯po，我問佢諗住覆邊個po又唔敢答<br />\n仲要小學雞到學人玩洗版屈毛<br />\n後尾扮係道歉但係繼續屈毛，講真時事台俾人叫cctoy咪就係有呢啲死賤種<br />\n<br />\n男星Daniel Kaluuya在「奧斯卡」領獎時，聲援「香港抗爭者」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504441</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e1f9a26f36c82fa9f8a23e4aaea434b78a692563","tid":2505013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3393b2157ace60327d3fc1b8f7ac38f650f494bb","tid":2505013,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396f48660a20abb3003f4c800196e886490691e1","tid":2505013,"uid":24596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"樓主似係黑警😰😰"},{"pid":"cc542658bd0aad67154015aa28ac5a88fd474af2","tid":2505013,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4da2275d933a9c2053162a074688e3d224bdc6","tid":2505013,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:10:13.